        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col info text-center">
                <h2>Blaze Rods Magenta Shulker Box</h2>
                <div class="col justify-content-center">
                    <img src="/images/pixel-craft/season-6/item-combinations/blaze-rods/magenta_shulker_box.png" alt="An image of the contents of the Magenta Shulker Box for the Blaze Rods."/>
                    <p>This is what is required for the Magenta Shulker Box in the Blaze Rods item. A text list of what is in the Magenta Shulker Box.</p>
